In Instagram scroll down till you see an AD
Save the post
Go to your account / Saved / All post -> the saved post(ad) is visible
Click on it -> The original post(ad) is displayed
Click on the 3 dots / Hide ad and select any of the listed options (only the "It`s irrelevant" option is tested)
Go back to your account / Saved / All post -> The ad is still listed, but:
  A, but the cover picture is blurred out
  B, clicking on it, the original post(ad) is not displayed
  C, not able to remove this item from the Saved list
  
  
  
  Please see the attachment for more information.
